OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be mostly cloudy and
OL,6,Frather cool over Shetland with a few
OL,7,Flight showers arriving from the north
OL,8,Fin the afternoon. Mainly dry and
OL,9,Fbright over Orkney.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry start with some clear
OL,12,Fspells for Orkney. Otherwise cloudy
OL,13,Fthrough the evening and overnight with
OL,14,Fa few light showers.
OL,15,
OL,16,CSaturday:FA cooler day with some
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells and variable
OL,18,Fcloud. Mostly dry but the odd light
OL,19,Fshower possible in the morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
