OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudier
OL,6,Fon Sunday with some showery outbreaks
OL,7,Fof rain. Variable cloud and bright
OL,8,Fspells Monday with chance of some
OL,9,Fshowers. Becoming drier again Tuesday
OL,10,Fwith variable cloud and sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
